                     <interp inst="t18280911-100-person676" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner some years; I only know that the conduct of his first wife was very bad, indeed most disgraceful; she conducted herself most disgraceful - he made a good husband and forgave her a good many times, till he was thought too indulgent.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 48.</p>
